# Darknet Diaries Theme V2.0

## Description

A Theme for the Hak5 WiFi Pineapple Pager - inspired by Darknet Diaries - Art used with permission from Jack Rhysider
Created by Nomaran

## Tested Firmware

Developed using the V1.0.4 Pager firmware and the V0.5 theme framework

## Features

A full recolor to match the Darknet Diaries assets
A Reworked dashboard
Customized icons and labels
Wardriving/Wigle dashboard for the on the go Pager
Custom animations

## Wardriving Dashboard

A simple dashboard for quick access to Wardriving resources.

### Features

Status fields for GPS
Toggle for Wigle
Toggle for PCAP
Restart GPSd
GPS Device
Baud Rate

