## Installion Instructions

### Direct Copy

#### Windows

If you are running a current version of Windows you can simply use the scp command:

`scp -r themes/darknet-diaries/ root@172.16.42.1:/root/themes/`

Otherwise you can use WinSCP program, an FTP program of your choice, or even using SSHFS: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O5Qz-hiYjlc. Ensure the theme is uploaded to 

`/root/themes`

Select the theme from Settings > Display > Theme

#### Linux/MacOS

`scp -r themes/darknet-diaries/ root@172.16.42.1:/root/themes/`

Select the theme from Settings > Display > Theme

### Directly on the Pager

Connect to the Virtual Pager or SSH in then run the following commands

`cd /root/`

`git clone https://github.com/hak5/wifipineapplepager-themes.git`

`cp -r wifipineapplepager-themes/themes/darknet-diaries /root/themes/`

Select the theme from Settings > Display > Theme

